{"tid":2162364,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"NVIDIA 落實 HK$4,055 億收購 ARM    預計夏季尾完成交易","createTime":"2020-08-18T05:46:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T10:37:03.000Z","uid":98659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7d70c3c094eb208edb11da7769baf01073e062c4","tid":2162364,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T05:46:12.000Z","msg":"SoftBank 創辦人兼社長孫正義早前證實正積極考慮於近期將 2016 年收購的 ARM 對外出售，而近年發展順利的 NVIDIA 可能為目前 ARM 最大的潛在買家。最新消息指，交易已進入倒數階段，並可能會在今年夏季完成，交易金額可望高達 400 億英鎊（約港幣 HK$4,055 億）。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n據英媒《Evening Standard》報導， SoftBank 與 NVIDIA 就 ARM 交易已進入最後談判階段，預計持續 30 至 45 天後可達共識，即最快將在月底完成交易，外界估計 NVIDIA 出價高達 400 億英鎊（約港幣 HK$4,055 億）。<br />\n<br />\n接受 SoftBank 委託出售 ARM 的外資 Goldman Sachs 一開始與 Apple 接洽，惟其沒興趣作出收購，之後 Goldman Sachs 試圖聯繫數家科技企業包括 Qualcomm、Google、Samsung 以及 NVIDIA 合資入股 ARM，不過最後僅剩 NVIDIA 感興趣。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nSoftBank 在 2016 年以 240 億英鎊收購 ARM，是次出售 ARM 的原因估計是去年的巨額虧損，包括 WeWork 在內的多項投資計劃導致軟銀出現約 95 億英鎊（約港幣 HK$963 億）的營運虧損。不過，外界分析，與其他上市晶片公司和科技公司過去 4 年的表現相較，SoftBank 以 400 億英鎊出售 ARM 其實獲利不高。<br />\n<br />\n另外，達成協議可能導致英日之間的貿易談判緊張，目前英國正積極與日本達成貿易協議以離開歐盟。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n資料來源：Evening Standard<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/08/18/nvidia-arm/fun-tech/?fbclid=IwAR07AyrX9Y6qmyacGpyMiqFJ_IMfXH-Tc2GaTtK_wAwOWusKrQ2E7OV-t5E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F08%2F18%2Fnvidia-arm%2Ffun-tech%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR07AyrX9Y6qmyacGpyMiqFJ_IMfXH-Tc2GaTtK_wAwOWusKrQ2E7OV-t5E&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkF6bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=4385abef\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/08/18/nvidia-arm/fun-tech/?fbclid=IwAR07AyrX9Y6qmyacGpyMiqFJ_IMfXH-Tc2GaTtK_wAwOWusKrQ2E7OV-t5E</a><br />\n<br />\n衝啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520ce6eb546c7e193e1610655c21c8a649fa4e31","tid":2162364,"uid":96068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T05:50:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有4股 <br />\n上阿！"},{"pid":"0ea09fe3ed1f623bbbcafa121da2cedb728d917e","tid":2162364,"uid":47239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:07:31.000Z","msg":"ARM唔係金蛋黎㗎咩？點解得Nvidia有興趣"},{"pid":"360b13ea3bea133dfc923470da214653b7b1d4c4","tid":2162364,"uid":81368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:08:11.000Z","msg":"冇買NVDIA <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0887e184361466df8bb2f4d123bb46914a7282d","tid":2162364,"uid":355887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:08:58.000Z","msg":"nvda又升空<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3768535d48abee55cea113b69610dd8786500191","tid":2162364,"uid":370541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T10:37:03.000Z","msg":"黃仁勳：NVIDIA 未提出收購 Arm 的計畫<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inside.com.tw/article/20738-Jen-Hsun-Huang-said-that-NVIDIA-has-not-proposed-a-plan-to-acquire-Arm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inside.com.tw%2Farticle%2F20738-Jen-Hsun-Huang-said-that-NVIDIA-has-not-proposed-a-plan-to-acquire-Arm&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkF6bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=50808ce1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inside.com.tw/article/20738-Jen-Hsun-Huang-said-that-NVIDIA-has-not-proposed-a-plan-to-acquire-Arm</a>"}]}